The Annual Town Budget Meeting shall be held on one of the first ten business days of May. The proposed budget shall be the only substantive matter presented to this Annual Town Budget Meeting for adoption pursuant to the provisions of this section. It is the intent of this Charter that the provisions of the General Statutes governing town meetings as contained in [[Section 7-7|https://www.cga.ct.gov/current/pub/chap_090.htm#sec_7-7]] shall not apply to the adoption of this budget.